SUMMARY:[Greater Orlando Volleyball Club] Summer Bash Coed Tournament (B/B
 B)
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260725T090000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260725T180000
UID:Greater_Orlando_Volleyball_Club-Summer_Bash_Coed_Tournament_(B/BB)-202
 6-07-25T09:00:00
DESCRIPTION:Summer Bash Tournament Details\n\nTournament Details\n\n- Date
 : July 25\, 2026\n- Time: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM  - One division tournament 
 goes from 9am to 6pm \n- Two division tournament will be split 9am - 6pm 
 and 12pm - 9pm\n\n- Location: Dover Shores Community Center\n- 8 Player Ma
 x Roster\n- Iron Middles Allowed\nTRUE COED FORMAT - 3 Men + 3 Women on th
 e court at all times\n\nCome hang & have a good day\n\n- Free entry for an
 yone to come watch\n- Snacks and drinks provided for everyone \n- Lunch p
 rovided for players\n\nEntry & Prizes\n\n- $250 registration per team \n-
  $500 cash prize for winner (subject to change with registration numbers)
  \n- Individual awards for group stage\n- Finals MVP award\n\nHow to Regi
 ster\n\n- Team captains sign up your full team to secure your spot.\n- Spo
 ts are limited and will fill quickly.\n\nSummer 2026\n\nMore info: https:/
 /goadultsportsleague.leagueapps.com/app/tournaments/5018478
LOCATION:Dover Shores Community Center
URL:https://goadultsportsleague.leagueapps.com/app/tournaments/5018478
END:VEVENT
