 - Finals MVP award\n\nHow to Register\n\n- Team captains sign up your full
  team to secure your spot.\n- Spots are limited and will fill quickly.\n\n
 Summer 2026\n\nMore info: https://goadultsportsleague.leagueapps.com/app/t
 ournaments/5018502
